snippet.title: GAAMI Making Video | Vishwak Sen | Chandini Chowdary | Vidyadhar Kagita | UV Creations
snippet.description:
GAAMI Making Video on UV Creations. #Gaami latest telugu movie starring Vishwak Sen, Chandini Chowdary and others chronicles the adventurous journey of Shankar- a wounded, reluctant and reclusive aghora on his quest to find the cure for his very rare human condition- the one that will be cured, only when he can confront and conquers the haunting ironical questions of his life.

snippet.title: LADDU | 1000 MOTICHOOR LADDU | Sweet and Soft Laddu Recipe Cooking in Village | Boondi Laddu Making
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook 1000 Motichoor Laddu using crushed pearls. Normally, laddu is made with Boondi, but Motichoor laddu is made using smashed Boondi. That is why Moticoor Laddu is special and so soft.

The taste is Yummy!

Neerparavai (transl.‚ÄâSeabird) is a 2012 Indian Tamil-language drama film written and directed by Seenu Ramasamy and produced by Udhayanidhi Stalin. It stars Vishnu and Sunaina, and Nandita Das plays the older version of the latter's character. Saranya Ponvannan, Samuthirakani, Varsha Ashwathi, and Anupama Kumar play supporting roles. snippet.title: Bana Hi Nahi Tha Jana - Dino James [Official Video] | @BluishMusic
snippet.description:
‚ÄúBana Hi Nahi Tha‚Äù is essentially a breakup ballad, a dreamy lo-fi tune. As the guy reflects on his experiences, he comes to the realization that he may not be cut out for love. It's not a matter of lacking love, as he certainly understands it. He fondly recalls moments with her, cherishing the time they shared. Unable to alter the past or rectify past mistakes, he grapples with regret. Nevertheless, he resolves to liberate himself from her love and the memories they shared, opting for autonomy.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.description:

Gaami, chronicles the adventurous journey of Shankar- a wounded, reluctant and reclusive aghora on his quest to find the cure for his very rare human condition- the one that will be cured, only when he can confront and conquers the haunting ironical questions of his life.

snippet.title: Rice Cake Recipe in Tamil | Soft and Spongy Arisi Cake | Kalathappam Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make rice cake recipe in tamil. This is a soft, spongy and fluffy cake which can be made with raw rice. This cake is sweetened with jaggery and the grated coconut adds some texture to the recipe. The added baking soda increases the air bubbles in the cake and makes it spongy. This cake / appam can be made in no time and tastes absolutely delicious. This recipe is also known as Kalathappam and is a traditional Kerala recipe.

#ricecake #arisicake #ricecakerecipe 

Friends, please do try this arisi cake recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

Ingredients:
1 cup Raw Rice (200g)
1/2 cup Water
1 cup grated Coconut
1/2 cup Water
1+3/4 cup powdered Jaggery (250g)
1/2 cup Water
little less than 1/2 tsp Baking Soda
pinch of Salt
2 tsp Ghee

snippet.description:

Khaie Episode 15 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Sparx Smartphones - Faysal Quraishi - Durefishan Saleem - 7th February 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Khaie Digitally Presented by Sparx Smartphones #shinewithsparx
Get Ready to be Enthralled by 'Khaie' - Brought to You by Geo TV with the Cutting-Edge Innovation of Sparx Smartphone as the Exclusive Digital Presenting Partner. A Spectacular Journey Awaits

The story is a revenge saga that unfolds against the backdrop of the ancient tradition of Khaie, where the male members of an enemy's family are eliminated to stop the continuation of their lineage.  At the center of this age-old vendetta are Darwesh Khan, Duraab Khan, and his son Channar Khan, with Zamdaa, the daughter of Darwesh, bearing the heaviest consequences.  
Darwesh Khan is haunted by his father's murder at the hands of Duraab Khan. Seeking a peaceful life, Darwesh aims to broker a truce to end generational enmity. However, suspicions arise, and Duraab Khan and his son Channar Khan doubt Darwesh's intentions for peace.
Despite the genuine efforts of Darwesh, a kind-hearted man with a message for peace, a tragic turn of events unfolds during a celebration at Darwesh's home, causing immense suffering for Zamdaa and her family.
Will Zamdaa bow down in front of her enemies? If not, then will Zamdaa be able to take revenge on her family culprits? Will Zamdaa find allies in her journey, or will she face her enemies alone?

Written By: Saqlain Abbas
Directed By: Syed Wajahat Hussain
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: Khaie Episode 14 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Sparx Smartphones - 6th February 2024
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khaie Episode 14 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Sparx Smartphones - Faysal Quraishi - Durefishan Saleem - 6th February 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Khaie Digitally Presented by Sparx Smartphones #shinewithsparx
Get Ready to be Enthralled by 'Khaie' - Brought to You by Geo TV with the Cutting-Edge Innovation of Sparx Smartphone as the Exclusive Digital Presenting Partner. A Spectacular Journey Awaits

The story is a revenge saga that unfolds against the backdrop of the ancient tradition of Khaie, where the male members of an enemy's family are eliminated to stop the continuation of their lineage.  At the center of this age-old vendetta are Darwesh Khan, Duraab Khan, and his son Channar Khan, with Zamdaa, the daughter of Darwesh, bearing the heaviest consequences.  
Darwesh Khan is haunted by his father's murder at the hands of Duraab Khan. Seeking a peaceful life, Darwesh aims to broker a truce to end generational enmity. However, suspicions arise, and Duraab Khan and his son Channar Khan doubt Darwesh's intentions for peace.
Despite the genuine efforts of Darwesh, a kind-hearted man with a message for peace, a tragic turn of events unfolds during a celebration at Darwesh's home, causing immense suffering for Zamdaa and her family.
Will Zamdaa bow down in front of her enemies? If not, then will Zamdaa be able to take revenge on her family culprits? Will Zamdaa find allies in her journey, or will she face her enemies alone?

Written By: Saqlain Abbas
Directed By: Syed Wajahat Hussain
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast:
Faysal Quraishi as Channar Khan

snippet.title: All India Rank | Official Trailer | Varun Grover | Sriram Raghavan | In Theatres 23rd Feb 2024
snippet.description:
Sriram Raghavan presents Masaan & Sacred Games writer Varun Grover's directorial debut ALL INDIA RANK. 

Releasing in theatres all over India on 23rd Feb 2024. 

A coming-of-age comedy-drama set in the late 90s - 17-year-old Lucknow boy Vivek Singh struggles with the ambitions & mediocrity of his parents while prepping for India‚Äôs toughest under-grad exam in an IIT coaching in Kota. A story of possible dreams and impossible competition.

Amanraj's Verse
Uka saawla sa rang
Naa koi chitta gora ae
Re wo gharkya ke bairi
Ekla hi chhora ae

Dil dil aali baat ne jabaan pe wo rakhe
Chhora khulli kitaab ka koi panna gora ae
Wo bhola bhaala bhi ae, wo mature bhi ghana
Chhora aatma ka re wo pure bhi ghana

Manne leja na churake uke paas te koi
Manne leke kayi baari insecure bhi ghana‚Ä¶

(Background Ragni‚Ä¶)

Belong chhora achhe parivaar te
Wo biggad sa lagge bas bahar te
Re jaana aaye gede uski gail me
Baba saam aale darbaar pe

Maanu su main chhora agressive thoda
Manne leke ho jawe se possesive thoda
Kyahe cheej ka na bairi manne rakhta toda
Lakha me ek mhara lagta joda

Jaya's Verse : 
Nice man, Such a nice man, Such a wise man 
Sach ae bolee sach dekhee eyes mein
It's like boy you came from outer world 
Our names were 2 now they're one word
I can't believe you were custom made for me
Oh God tell me what's the thing that rare in me
You gave the whole cosmos in my arms .. In my arms

Canada America koise videsh me
Une le jaungi apne main base pe
Yade khud ka to uka kise gel rola na
Khali yaaran piche aawe roz naam case me

Ho aaj kaal uke gaane vaane chalre ghane
Une log-baag aaj kal jaanre ghane
Uki kaamyabi gelya meri fikar bhi badhi
Log nazara ne upe taanre ghare‚Ä¶

Amanraj Gill Rap :

Karde hai wo he
Jo bhi mann me wo thaan‚Äôta
Rapiye paisya ne chhora
Kuch bhi na maanta

Nyu to jaane se une Duniya ya bohat
Par mere te zyada usne Koi na jaanta

Pyaar mere tayi Ek bol pe rahve hai
Baat kare na kare Chhora call pe rahve hai

Wallpaper pe laarya daaki meri gel photo
Shareaam chhora mere dil ki wall pe rahve

Main to aam si hu kati
Une jaane saara shehar
Haath pakde wo mera
Mere kamb jawe paer

Manne lagge adhoora sab uske bagair
Re main khaa ke marr jau, chhora lagge mane zehar re‚Ä¶

Jaya's Verse :
Baby take me higher That's what I desire 
You & me are fire Let's sing this song as choir
O yar tu leke chal mannee teri nagari mein
